project_descr: To quickly respond to emerging needs of the areas which were under Islamic State of Iraq and Levant control, this project supports the short and medium term stabilization and early recovery requirements within the longer term Local Area Development.

outputs.output_descr: Iraqi Government is supported to address the immediate stabilization and recovery needs in newly accessible areas which allows for the sustainable return of Internally Displaced Persons
donor_name: UNITED STATES AGENCY FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (USAID)

outputs.output_descr: FFES will undertake medium-scale projects that strengthen public infrastructure and services such as hospitals, universities, etc., generate large numbers of jobs and help consolidate corridors between stabilized cities and districts.
